text: Brandon Clagette (born April 30, 2002) is an American soccer player who plays for the Pittsburgh Panthers in the NCAA Division I. == Club career == On July 13, 2019, Clagette appeared for Atlanta United 2, the USL Championship affiliate of Atlanta United FC, starting in an 8–1 loss to New York Red Bulls II. == References == == External links == * Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:People from Douglasville, Georgia Category:Sportspeople from the Atlanta metropolitan area Category:Soccer players from Georgia (U.S. state) Category:American soccer players Category:Association football defenders Category:Pittsburgh Panthers men's soccer players Category:Atlanta United 2 players Category:USL Championship players
